            <title>[LU-2291] Improve racer test load</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2291</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are some improvements that could be done to the racer.sh test load, so that it is trying even more wild &amp;amp; wacky things at the same time:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;use &lt;tt&gt;lfs setstripe&lt;/tt&gt; to create files across multiple OSTs&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;use &lt;tt&gt;lfs mkdir&lt;/tt&gt; to create directories on remote MDTs (OSF-105 to land on master with DNE)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;run racer.sh on all of the mounted clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
